Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:09.19,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.92,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:47.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.63,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.31,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.10,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯·穆罕默德的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那個英雄的傳聞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，聽聞那個達哈魯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近帶著他的Pharaoh Gundam Ⅳ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在neo Egypt這裡出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有很多人看見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定是在這種刮起大風沙的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個地球被極度污染的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Egypt這裡也留有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代王國興盛時的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，不只那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個可怕的傳說流傳下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當世上刮起戰鬥風暴時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的Fighter的靈魂會和怨念一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從漫長的沉睡中甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的對手是從墳墓來的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Egypt的Pharaoh Gundam Ⅳ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思議的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱它的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯·穆罕默德已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的！你或許會那樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個亡靈或許握有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Devil Gundam一起降落地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙的哥哥京二的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}恐怖！亡靈Fighter出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很嚴重…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有生還者！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，準備治療
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，振作！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他出現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該已經死了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家全死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰的所為？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛艙被一擊毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法這麼殘忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！你看！GUNDAM FIGHT啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT也還未宣佈開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我堂堂正正現身吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想攻擊駕駛艙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算不給我反擊的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的Dragon Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，對手是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Egypt的GUNDAM！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我們剛才看見的殘骸，究竟是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我要幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！飛龍炎旗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT國際條約第二條
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可攻擊對手的駕駛艙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我殺了他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親手殺了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了，地點應該沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…說笑吧，多蒙老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，neo Egypt的GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確在這裡被擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和成員一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，多蒙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，下午和蔡齋西交手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個GUNDAM究竟是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…幽靈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是幽靈，被纏住的是蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊！老兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說完這麼危言聳聽的話就走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一晚也好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最怕這種事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和那件事有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要曾在這裡的GUNDAM殘骸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有Devil Gundam三大理論機能之一的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我再生！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你哥哥果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！別叫那傢伙做我哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我不會再那樣叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無心殺你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要尿褲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西說他看見木仍伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃伊！木乃伊呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去哪裡啊？姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墳墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Egypt成員的最後一句話是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從那句話著手調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查到，達哈魯·穆罕默德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是第三屆GUNDAM FIGHT的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個曾為neo Egypt帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統治世界實權的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是為傳頌他這個英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而建的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，幽靈的真正身份是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的GUNDAM Fighter嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣，我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不進去…！我想回去啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事和GUNDAM FIGHT無關啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著復興少林寺重任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被幽靈嚇成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠雲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞山！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以後怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰森恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方一定會有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西！   多蒙先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，總算沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已說過不來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯，是達哈魯的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄，你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說，打開達哈魯的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！老兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做會受到懲罰的！住手…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手呀！老兄！老兄呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西，你看看裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不看…！我好怕…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不看…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見，棺材裡是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那個木乃伊果然是達哈魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶莉茵走！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何攻擊蔡齋西！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我打！怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，用那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！收拾木乃伊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，他是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西，雖然我不知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他看來對你還未死心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看來只好跟他決一勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…拒絕啊…又不是正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少林寺的繼承人怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這點事就畏縮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是neo China的恥辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼！？蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管後退的話無法比賽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？蔡齋西！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點攻擊便令你招架不來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣，要鼓起勇氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…身體不能動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你想辦法幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，還不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯為何要攻擊蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快知道原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了，不出我所料！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵小姐，那是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到詳情是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西，仔細聽我們講
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切源自40年前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三屆GUNDAM FIGHT的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情源自四年後的第四屆大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯的GUNDAM在決賽裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被對手弄得身首異處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時，連駕駛艙也發生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的對手就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們少林寺上兩代的住持大師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是你爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是被少林寺戰士打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯的Fighter意識…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，一定是他身為Fighter的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望再次比賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成木乃伊也想繼續比賽的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達哈魯肉體滅亡後也在繼續比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定要以Fighter的身份回應他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！GUNDAM FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶花教典·十絕陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我收拾他！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好！蔡齋西！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次，你安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這究竟是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開，蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等這機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是什麼怪物！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西，你不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，能和本應死了的達哈魯一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令GUNDAM不斷復活的自我再生機能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是…透過京二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了Devil Gundam的能力！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這隻手在閃耀和咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在叫我打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是包含了愛、憤怒和悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙又變成那樣子…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是King Of Heart，多蒙·卡休嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連達哈魯單純的Fighter的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被變成邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Devil Gundam接觸後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連死人也會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白啊…老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭，莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…對方是你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:31.50,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:35.89,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:40.33,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨著 追求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:43.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:51.05,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人啊 在我瞳孔的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:56.75,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實搖曳著的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:02.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何傳達才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:08.54,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓受傷的心與身體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:12.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:18.71,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在煙雨濛濛的neo Turkey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵同過去的戀人重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，最可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經成為了Devil Gundam的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵究竟能否把他從魔爪中拯救出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動武鬥傳G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨中再會…Falling Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


